commits.message:
EUCA-8707, EUCA-7983: Fix partition lookup error wrt internal services.

A ServiceConfiguration can be all of:
  1. A child in the partition of another component (e.g.,
     NodeController and the ClusterController).
  2. Have no ENABLED service in it's partition.
  3. Need to know the name of it's partition.

In the case that NodeController component calls here prior to knowing
 it's partition.  If the ClusterController is not ENABLED this will
 fail and deliver a meaningless message.

EUCA-8707, EUCA-7983: Fix DescribeServices response handling.

The ClusterController proxy state falsely assumed that any reported
data would always pertain to it.  Also, incomplete data was not
handled properly.
